{"id":148281,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/04/洛桑森格愿意同北京对话/","date":"2011-04-28T08:00:24Z","modified":"2011-04-28T08:00:24Z","title":"洛桑森格愿意同北京对话","content":"<div>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">华盛顿</span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">据德国国际通讯社（</span><span>dapd</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">）报道，西藏流亡政府新当选领导人洛桑森格（</span><span>Lobsang Sangay</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">，前译洛桑桑盖，现据西藏流亡政府网上公告修正）相信，达赖喇嘛有朝一日能重返家乡。本周三（</span><span>4</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">月</span><span>27</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">日）被正式宣布当选为西藏流亡政府下届首席噶伦（首席部长，即总理）的这位美国哈佛学者对媒体表示，他本人将致力于实现达赖喇嘛关于藏人获得更多自主权的愿望。他称，西藏流亡政府已做好同中国进行对话的准备。作为流亡政府新首脑，洛桑森格将承接达赖喇嘛迄今扮演的政治角色。达赖喇嘛此前宣布，不再担任流亡藏人政治领袖，但愿意保留精神领袖地位。洛桑森格将于8月14日</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">之前在流亡政府所在地的印度达兰萨拉宣誓就职。诺贝尔和平奖得主达赖喇嘛</span><span>1959</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">年流亡西藏。他不寻求西藏独立，但要求有</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">“</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">真正的自治</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">”</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">。</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n</div>\n<p><img src=\"http://api.mixpanel.com/track/?data=eyJldmVudCI6ICJmdWxsdGV4dGltcHJlc3Npb24iLCAicHJvcGVydGllcyI6IHsidG9rZW4iOiAiYTRhNDYwYTM5MDRlZWU4ZmY1ZTAyNGVhNGJkZTdhYzIifX0=&#038;ip=1&#038;img=1\" width=\"1\" height=\"1\" border=\"0\" /><img src=\"http://pixel.quantserve.com/pixel/p-89EKCgBk8MZdE.gif\" border=\"0\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" /><a href=\"http://fulltextrssfeed.com\"><img src=\"http://fulltextrssfeed.com/images/1x1.gif\" border=\"0\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" alt=\"ftrf - full text rss\" /></a><a href=\"http://api.mixpanel.com/track/?data=eyJldmVudCI6ICJmdWxsdGV4dGNsaWNrIiwgInByb3BlcnRpZXMiOiB7InRva2VuIjogImE0YTQ2MGEzOTA0ZWVlOGZmNWUwMjRlYTRiZGU3YWMyIn19&#038;ip=1&#038;redirect=http://talkita.com/wrap?url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw-world.de%2Fdw%2Farticle%2F0%2C%2C15034096%2C00.html%3Fmaca%3Dchi-rss-chi-all-1127-rdf&#038;title=%E6%B4%9B%E6%A1%91%E6%A3%AE%E6%A0%BC%E6%84%BF%E6%84%8F%E5%90%8C%E5%8C%97%E4%BA%AC%E5%AF%B9%E8%AF%9D\">Chat about this story w/ Talkita</a></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://www.feedblitz.